            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are tender, add a knob of <strong>butter </strong>with a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>and<strong> </strong>roughly crush with a fork – these are your <strong>crushed potatoes</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
